<br>
KC on the other hand is pretty light.  If you're really worried, say on the borderline of dubious faction, /con everything as it comes in.  Anything that is not scowls will be a small faction hit.  Really, the only things I've noticed much on are the large model drolvargs, (little guys are freebie kills), and Slixin Klex and a few named undead.  Funny thing about KC is that I've been on both sets of epic raids there, several times, but I don't think I've actually taken a VS hit from killing either version of VS.<br>
<br>
Fixing VS once you're Kos is a pain.  Usually you have to take out Kunark dragons in large numbers, (3 opportunities for most of us, on a pretty long spawn cycle).  You could also try VP, which I hear is good faction, but I'm not sure if it's everything in there, or if you just get nice, large faction hits from dropping the dragons.  Either way, not pretty.<br>
<br>
Zerlatik Flaimweaver<br>
Sorcerer of Tholuxe Paells<br>
